59 (13) MAYOR. The individual elected or appointed to the
60 official position of mayor of the city.
61 (14) OPEN-COMPETITIVE. The process of seeking qualified
62 candidates for a regular position from any qualified
63 individual including taking applications from the general
64 public and other employees in the regular service not
65 otherwise in the department for which the position exists.
66 (15) PAY GRADE. The specific pay range set forth in the
67 pay plan for a classification.
