75 regular position from a reemployment list, promotion list, or
76 eligible register who has not completed his or her
77 probationary period.
78 (20) PROMOTION. An advancement from one class to
79 another related occupational class with increased duties or
80 responsibilities, or both, and for which a higher rate of pay
81 is prescribed.
82 (21) PUBLIC HEARING. A meeting of the board, open to
83 the public, at which any resident, taxpayer, or party at
84 interest may appear and may be heard.
