561 city shall make or approve any payment for personal services
562 to any individual holding a position in the regular service
563 not otherwise exempt from this act unless the position was
564 filled from a certified list of eligibles approved by the
565 director. The director may refuse to certify the payroll,
566 voucher, or account of any ineligible individual found to be
